Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:01.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得那些家伙会不会来医院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是一脸不相信的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会信才怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 他们一定会来袭击人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么就能这样断言？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 就之前的病例来看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会一下子杀死牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠在8月12日因贫血倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后病情逐渐恶化 15日死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之间隔了4天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:34.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 可以认为她被吸了4次血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4次？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:40.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说 人如果失去超过50%的循环血液量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会导致心脏停止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:46.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设血液量共4升 那就是2升
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:52.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙大概一次也吸不了2升血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们喝不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:58.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说他们的饭量只有这么2杯左右
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:03.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设 1次的吸血量是这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2次袭击就会引起休克症状
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4次就会造成心脏停止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:12.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 实际上应该没有这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 被吸血的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便睡着了也会被惊醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么牺牲者什么都不说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说不说 不如说是被什么禁言了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:23.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像某种昆虫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:30.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好会在吸血时 注入类似麻药的物质
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 那些家伙就能操纵牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:40.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:46.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病情稳定了 至少没有恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小律 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:53.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是节子婆婆的早饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:56.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然她没有要吃的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过生命体征已经稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她住院应该是做对了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:07.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安代小姐 我们不值夜班真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧 医生都说不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出诊工作上午有2个 下午…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下午有1个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:35.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生 节子婆婆怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问病情吗 还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些 今天也拜托各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:45.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节子婆婆的具体治疗方案 定下了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒没有 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问怎么了 大家都很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:56.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生一个人值夜班也太勉强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不让我们帮忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您的意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:11.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方案决定后 会请你们帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:16.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安代小姐 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来真的很累嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:36.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子 你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:39.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被母亲叫来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:43.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说是你让我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:45.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:49.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我为工作奔忙 感到疲惫不堪」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:52.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「既然是我老婆 这种时候就该待在家里」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把店关了给我回来」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:57.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我马上就知道她是骗我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:01.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回去就回去吧 反正你不在也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你在家我也没空陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:08.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回什么啊 我都在店里贴了暂时关店的通知了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 看妈妈的心情转好 你就挑时机回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不说我也会那么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能让你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:23.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子 你好歹也是尾崎家的儿媳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:27.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫为工作奔忙 你却想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人要知廉耻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失言了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:36.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没想到母亲您会躲在一旁偷听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫 你怎么就这么忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子里发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:49.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断有人死亡 不会是传染病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:52.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:57.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 看起来像是传染病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:58.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:04.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听好了 以后再有那种患者就叫救护车送到别的医院去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:08.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没必要做危险的事 好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什么好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:15.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫 你是历史悠久的尾崎家的独苗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一你有个好歹 医院怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:20.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为某人总不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连个继承家业的人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:27.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万不得已的话 从亲戚中收养个能干的孩子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:31.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 妈妈再婚怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出诊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还露着大腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:40.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊 死老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴 给我有教养一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被偷听的老太婆这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:47.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能偷吃哦 绿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生他在医院留宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:03.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为工务店的节子婆婆住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我给他做些慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节子婆婆也病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:10.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家人怎么了啊 一个接一个的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐还真是勤快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那位年轻夫人来做不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回来了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我看到那个人的车了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子小姐不是会做这种事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老太太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:29.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少住持在陪医生留宿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老太太讨厌那间寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为比尾崎家还有声望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:43.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎 你也要去散步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 算了 我一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:13.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙拥有多大的能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会能变成蝙蝠 还会穿墙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:25.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电影里 想击退他们就得用十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:28.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们怕十字架和大蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:31.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在镜子里照不出来 害怕阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:36.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对吸血鬼的认识 都是编造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:41.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在这个村子里有一群吸血杀人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:20.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:29.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙 只要抓住其中一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能快点找到办法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能进行解剖什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解剖？等下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:38.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的有吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:43.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了要吸血 别的都和生前没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静信 这里是二楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:12:59.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:01.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这扇窗的外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:05.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有可供踩踏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:31.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不允许你随便进入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:52.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节子婆婆 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天由我做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:04.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起昨天 今天您的心情似乎也好了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:15.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住院后第3天 节子婆婆的意识变得清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体不适的状况也改善了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会成为康复的首例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:24.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚睡得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 深夜时有醒来过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦话也说得相当清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为有谁在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:38.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 梦话什么的真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来 也许是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪回来的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下段日子是奈绪的四十九日了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}四十九日：日本的一种法事 死后每7天一次直至轮至49日\N此法事对死者前往极乐净土有重要意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:50.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是我太在意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:55.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想起来 可能是前天吧 也可能更早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段时间 一直清晰地做着这种梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那该不会是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:13.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:19.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果奈绪能回来的话 那该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有进 干康也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:22.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:33.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活着没？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要吃红豆馅面包？来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闷死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:49.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有工作到快死的男人和刁蛮婆婆 我真是嫁错了人家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃红豆馅面包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:16:00.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫君 少住持 我差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:01.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:04.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节子的状况好转了 我也安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:07.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:14.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好睡 尽量早点康复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就只剩下对方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于睡熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:37.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙施的催眠术应该也失效了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得奈绪今天也会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当她会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 如果能知道那些家伙的弱点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:52.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 吸血鬼的传说中有这么一说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:55.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼的话 如果不被邀请 就不能进入人类的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 如果不说「来我家玩吧」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就进不了人类的家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:06.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果邀请了 那房子就会对吸血鬼开放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天奈绪没有进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这样的话就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:15.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停电？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:20.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 村里的灯火没有灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:21.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能他们的夜视能力比较强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗对我们不利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:28.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得一楼好像有旧发电机来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:29.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去开启它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:31.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 静信 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:38.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候不是经常在医院里玩探险游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:01.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外面来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:14.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要去 奈绪在叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:20.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:48.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不进来袭击我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去的话就会被杀了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 是进不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节子婆婆 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:08.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以进来哦 只要有人邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:23.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 尾崎医生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:28.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫辰巳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:37.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫 发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:40.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会杀你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为吩咐过了 我还不能对医生下手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节…节子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:10.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:39.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那些尸变者打算今天一口气解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:43.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道我们藏起了节子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以速战速决以免夜长梦多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了要救她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:20:59.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:01.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能先回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:08.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:29.72,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}大きな夢 目指し歩いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:29.72,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}向着远大的梦想前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:40.23,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}迷い迷って 終わりのない旅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:40.23,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充满迷惑的无尽的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:52.00,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あの時は雪まじりの雨で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:52.00,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那时候雨雪交织
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:58.05,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}涙かどうか分からなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:58.05,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}落下的是不是眼泪无从知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:05.99,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}さよなら もう二度と会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:05.99,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永别了 已经不会再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:12.42,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私が選んだミライヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:12.42,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}朝向我选择的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:18.11,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}また一歩踏み出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:18.11,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又向前踏出了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:23.72,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}大きな 壁を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:23.72,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}跨过高大的墙壁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:29.39,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好きだったのにどうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:29.39,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}明明是喜欢的 但为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:34.83,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「最期だ」なんて言ったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:34.83,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要说「最后」两个字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:39.85,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今ではちゃんと分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:39.85,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如今我完全理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:42.87,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:42.87,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:48.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ねぇ "Walk" 強く…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:48.84,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗯 要坚定地走下去…
